item.title: boAt Rockerz 333 Upto 30 Hours Battery Bluetooth Headset (Teal Green, In the Ear)
item.dc:creator: imran
item.description: You can listen to your favourite tracks, play games, and attend calls in exceptional quality audio with the realme Buds Wireless 3 Neckband. With its ability to provide up to a 360-degree spatial audio effect, this neckband offers a captivating and immersive sound experience reminiscent of being in a theatre, where the sound envelops you from all directions. This feature creates a life-like and three-dimensional audio environment that boosts your senses. Additionally, sporting sophisticated Active Noise Cancellation (ANC) technology, this neckband allows you to indulge in a personalised auditory experience.
